**Professional tax** (PT) is a state-level tax levied on employment income. It is deductible from your gross salary and also allowed as a deduction under Section 16 of the Income Tax Act when computing taxable income. PT rates and slabs differ by state — Maharashtra charges up to ₹2,500/year, while some states like Delhi do not levy PT.
